videos.headline: Olivier Nkamhoua makes a nice cut for a Vols bucket
videos.description: Olivier Nkamhoua makes a nice cut and gets to the basket for an early Tennessee bucket.

videos.headline: Jacob Toppin grabs a transition bucket for Kentucky
videos.description: Cason Wallace gets the steal and finds Jacob Toppin in transition for a Kentucky bucket.

videos.headline: CJ Fredrick knocks down a Kentucky 3-pointer
videos.description: CJ Fredrick gets the Kentucky 3-pointer to fall as the Wildcats take an early lead vs. Tennessee.

videos.headline: Tshiebwe says defense carried UK past No. 5 UT
videos.description: Following a 63-56 upset win over the Volunteers, Oscar Tshiebwe says the Wildcats had a different level of focus and energy on the defensive end.
